1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:04,380
(Episode 136)

2
00:00:05,940 --> 00:00:09,080
(Order of Compulsory Eviction)

3
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:22,160
You'll have to get out of this house now.

4
00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:24,330
Get out of my house right now.

5
00:00:25,630 --> 00:00:29,230
Jung Suk Hee, you caused a scene
at the office, and now this?

6
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,400
Why should I leave my own house?
Are you crazy?

7
00:00:31,470 --> 00:00:32,570
Your house?

8
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:36,240
This is my father's house,
and it's filled with memories of Seo Rin.

9
00:00:36,510 --> 00:00:40,380
I can't stand to see a devil like you
living here any longer,

10
00:00:40,610 --> 00:00:42,680
so get out.
Get out of my house, right now.

11
00:00:42,750 --> 00:00:44,050
Have you lost your mind?

12
00:00:44,050 --> 00:00:46,350
Why would this be your house?
You're not making any sense.

13
00:00:46,350 --> 00:00:49,220
This house does belong to Jung Suk Hee.

14
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,530
Chairman Ma officially transferred it
to her.

15
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:55,690
But Chairman Ma collapsed
and is unconscious.

16
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:58,930
- How could he transfer the house?
- Before he collapsed,

17
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:02,400
he froze his assets, this house
and his personal accounts, in a trust.

18
00:01:02,970 --> 00:01:06,370
All control was given
to his biological daughter, Ma Eun Hye,

19
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:07,410
and Oh Jang Mi,

20
00:01:07,470 --> 00:01:09,740
on the condition
that they would be granted full authority.

21
00:01:09,810 --> 00:01:14,250
Now that the paternity suit is over,
my mom is legally...

22
00:01:14,510 --> 00:01:16,650
Grandfather's daughter, Ma Eun Hye.
Chae Hwa Young.

23
00:01:16,980 --> 00:01:20,080
So get out of my mom's house.

24
00:01:20,220 --> 00:01:24,160
What are you people talking about?
This is my house. I live here.

25
00:01:24,390 --> 00:01:26,490
Who do you think you are,
telling me to get out?

26
00:01:26,490 --> 00:01:27,530
Don't mess with me.

27
00:01:27,530 --> 00:01:30,560
Well, Chae Hwa Young,
it's not like you'll need a house anyway.

28
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:34,330
You'll be spending your life in prison.

29
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:35,370
Shut up.

30
00:01:35,670 --> 00:01:39,040
Who says I'm going to prison?
You're the one who's going to prison.

31
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,370
This is a warning.

32
00:01:40,370 --> 00:01:42,470
We are proceeding
with the forced eviction.

33
00:01:42,670 --> 00:01:43,780
Vacate the premises immediately.

34
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:46,410
I'm not leaving. Why should I?
I'm not leaving.

35
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:49,080
If you continue to refuse
or delay this eviction,

36
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:51,720
you can be charged
with Obstruction of Official Duties...

37
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:56,250
under Article 136 of the Criminal Code
and be arrested on the spot.

38
00:01:56,520 --> 00:02:00,690
Fine. It'd be better if you got arrested
instead of just leaving.

39
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:04,130
That way, we can go straight
to the police station...

40
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,860
and expose all the crimes
you've committed.

41
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:06,970
What?

42
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:10,130
Listen to you just running your mouth.

43
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,470
Suit yourself.

44
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:14,710
That'll save us the trouble.

45
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:18,480
Kang Nam Bong,
you should get your things and get out.

46
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:21,110
You don't want to get dragged...

47
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:23,150
to the police station with Chae Hwa Young.

48
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:25,250
You divorced me knowing all of this?

49
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,990
Did you set me up for this?

50
00:02:28,090 --> 00:02:29,720
You were the one constantly
demanding a divorce.

51
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,590
How dare you accuse me of setting you up?

52
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,090
Shut up and get out now.

53
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:38,000
You're nothing but a trespasser here.

54
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:39,930
This woman is unbelievable.

55
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,570
All right, go ahead and proceed
with the eviction.

56
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:56,280
Hong Ju, are we being kicked out too?

57
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,880
I don't think this applies to us.

58
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:01,020
Mom, you're the Chairman's mistress.

59
00:03:01,090 --> 00:03:02,520
My goodness.

60
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,860
How can you think about me like that?

61
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:10,960
Anyway, whatever it takes,
we have to cling to this house.

62
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:13,700
We have to. Understand?

63
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,140
Mom.

64
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:28,710
Grandfather will wake up soon.
Don't be too upset.

65
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:32,950
I don't know how to make
that witch Chae Hwa Young pay.

66
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:37,560
No matter what evidence we have,
she always wriggles out of it like a rat.

67
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,960
It won't be so easy for her this time.

68
00:03:40,330 --> 00:03:42,260
I made sure that even Detective Lee,

69
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,600
who was Chae Hwa Young's puppet,
could no longer cover for her.

70
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:47,130
And I've reported
the former prosecutor general,

71
00:03:47,130 --> 00:03:48,570
who had the most influence,

72
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:51,400
for his corruption,
so he'll be caught for something soon.

73
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,610
Good.

74
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:56,610
By the way, back when you were framed,

75
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:59,580
didn't they destroy
the evidence you submitted?

76
00:04:00,950 --> 00:04:03,080
Then will the investigation
into Father's attempted murder...

77
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,920
be closed for good?

78
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:09,190
Jin Hong Ju might have the evidence.

79
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,290
She helped Chae Hwa Young back then.

80
00:04:12,090 --> 00:04:13,730
I'll look into everything,

81
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:16,030
so don't you worry, Mom.

82
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:21,700
Looks like the battery
in this clock is dead.

83
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,580
Mom,

84
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:38,980
isn't this a spy camera?

85
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:42,490
You mean Father installed a hidden camera?

86
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:47,060
Grandfather must have put it here
as a precaution...

87
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,490
in case Chae Hwa Young tried something.

88
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:50,300
I've never seen this before.

89
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,460
He must have installed it recently.

90
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,970
Let's check it right away.

91
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:59,000
You...

92
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:08,450
(Stock Transfer Agreement)

93
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,980
(A: Ma Dae Chang, B: Ma Seo Rin)

94
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:21,860
You've clung so tenaciously to life.

95
00:05:22,990 --> 00:05:25,930
Now, let me be the one to sever it.

96
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:36,410
Goodness. That witch did this to Father...

97
00:05:36,570 --> 00:05:40,850
She hit Grandfather with a golf club.
That monster, Chae Hwa Young.

98
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:52,060
I can't believe this.

99
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:54,560
I suspected Chae Hwa Young did it,

100
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:56,930
but I never imagined
she'd do this to the Chairman.

101
00:05:57,060 --> 00:06:00,200
Grandfather and Seo Rin lived
with Chae Hwa Young for 30 years.

102
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:03,740
They might have even been closer
than blood relatives.

103
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:06,170
I don't understand
how she could be so cruel.

104
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,740
This is crucial.

105
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:09,640
With this video,
we can put Chae Hwa Young away...

106
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,040
for attempted murder.

107
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,510
If we're going to use this
with the other evidence we've gathered,

108
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,880
we need to completely cut off
her powerful backers.

109
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,250
Detective Lee alone won't be enough.

110
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,380
Let's go.

111
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:23,220
To put the squeeze on
the former prosecutor general...

112
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:24,320
who's backing Chae Hwa Young.

113
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,590
Did you get info on his corruption
from the private detective agency?

114
00:06:26,590 --> 00:06:30,190
Yes, he won't be able to cover
for Chae Hwa Young anymore.

115
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,170
Who are you people?

116
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:44,840
You may be retired,

117
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:47,810
but you were once the head
of the nation's judiciary.

118
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:53,020
You seem to have lost your mind,
so I brought a gift to help you find it.

119
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,190
What's this?

120
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:10,900
Babe, just a minute.

121
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:17,480
A devoted husband and a family man.

122
00:07:17,910 --> 00:07:20,780
You have a reputation for having
a spotless private life.

123
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:23,380
So how is it you live
the complete opposite of that?

124
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,850
With this,
forget about a career in politics.

125
00:07:25,850 --> 00:07:27,950
You'll be fired from the law firm
you're currently working for.

126
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:31,360
How dare you threaten me?

127
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:32,960
Do you have any idea who I am?

128
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:34,790
As a former prosecutor general,

129
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,230
you've been making
a nice profit pulling strings...

130
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,730
for your juniors still in office.

131
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:42,400
How about we leak that to the press,
along with this cheating scandal?

132
00:07:42,970 --> 00:07:45,970
That would be a fatal blow
to your political ambitions.

133
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:49,640
What do you want? Money?

134
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:52,280
Whatever Chae Hwa Young asks of you,

135
00:07:52,710 --> 00:07:54,650
stop backing her.

136
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,950
Chae Hwa Young.

137
00:07:57,010 --> 00:08:00,720
Cut all ties with Chae Hwa Young,
starting right now.

138
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:04,920
If you ever cover for her
or lift a single finger to help,

139
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,190
these photos and your lobbying records...

140
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:09,760
will be on the front page
of every paper in the country.

141
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:13,730
Start by blocking Chae Hwa Young's number.

142
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,830
I trust we've made ourselves clear.

143
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:19,400
Behave yourself
so we don't have to meet again.

144
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:27,610
I won't disappoint Chairman Martin Jang.

145
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:29,410
You can count on it.

146
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:33,350
Chairman Jang is fond of parties.

147
00:08:34,050 --> 00:08:36,350
He's suggested
a party attire dress code...

148
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:37,820
for the company's founding
anniversary event.

149
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,290
Party attire
for the founding anniversary event?

150
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:42,730
Okay, I understand.

151
00:08:42,890 --> 00:08:46,100
I'll let the planning team know,
so we can throw a lavish party.

152
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,870
Please tell Chairman Martin
that I have a request for him as well.

153
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:54,770
Please make sure no rumors get started...

154
00:08:54,970 --> 00:08:56,640
about me taking kickbacks from the sale.

155
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,440
Yes.

156
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,580
I'll expect the money to come in...

157
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:02,510
on the day
of the founding anniversary event.

158
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:04,050
I will see you then.

159
00:09:05,050 --> 00:09:06,050
Okay.

160
00:09:06,050 --> 00:09:07,990
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

161
00:09:07,990 --> 00:09:09,790
I'm going crazy with anxiety,

162
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,920
and he's talking about a party.
What a joke.

163
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,760
So they're definitely sending the money?

164
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:17,300
Yes. I had no choice but to use the money
they've put into the corporate account...

165
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:20,130
to keep the hotel from going bankrupt.

166
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:23,600
They will send us the kickback
on the day of the anniversary event,

167
00:09:23,970 --> 00:09:27,270
so sell off what you can of my assets.

168
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:30,580
Liquidate everything.
Scrape together every last cent...

169
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,640
and have it ready.

170
00:09:31,810 --> 00:09:33,010
Yes, understood.

171
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,580
D-day for us
leaving the country will be...

172
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,820
on the day
of the founding anniversary event.

173
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:39,880
Got it?

174
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:51,300
Are the founding anniversary event
preparations going smoothly?

175
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:55,170
We're going to hold a grand event
without a single hitch.

176
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:57,270
Make sure it's done right. Got it?

177
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:01,770
You know the company's situation, ma'am.

178
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:03,640
Why are you worried about that?

179
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:07,310
Director Kang.
Are the preparations going well?

180
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,320
The founding anniversary?

181
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:13,820
All right, I'll get it ready.

182
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:17,520
Let's see if Chae Hwa Young
will still be smiling that day.

183
00:10:21,290 --> 00:10:22,290
Dad.

184
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:24,630
How did you get here...

185
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:27,500
- Oh, please have a seat.
- Thanks.

186
00:10:35,410 --> 00:10:36,510
Oh Jang Mi.

187
00:10:37,110 --> 00:10:38,680
I misunderstood you all this time.

188
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:40,640
I apologize.

189
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,550
And...

190
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:49,520
Here is proof that
Chae Hwa Young murdered Oh Bok Gil.

191
00:10:50,450 --> 00:10:54,930
When Chae Hwa Young was talking to me,
I was using a burner phone.

192
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:59,000
So this is the burner phone
you used to talk to Chae Hwa Young?

193
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,930
On the night of the accident,

194
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:03,600
I received a message from her
asking me to come to the resort,

195
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:05,070
and I went right away.

196
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:08,370
Dad, so you got into that accident
while rushing to see Chae Hwa Young?

197
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:11,710
Yes, after I got Chae Hwa Young's message.

198
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:16,910
Maybe I was probably excited
on my way there.

199
00:11:17,650 --> 00:11:19,980
- On a quiet country road,
- Oh, no...

200
00:11:20,050 --> 00:11:21,690
by the time I saw something,

201
00:11:22,650 --> 00:11:24,190
it was already too late.

202
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,660
I'm sorry, Oh Jang Mi.

203
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:34,670
Baek Ho.

204
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:38,070
I'm so ashamed.

205
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:43,770
I was so caught up in my shallow love
that I ignored the truth all this time.

206
00:11:44,810 --> 00:11:47,110
Thank you for bringing me the evidence,

207
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:48,880
even now.

208
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,880
On that phone,

209
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:53,350
there's a recording...

210
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:57,220
of my conversation with Chae Hwa Young
from the day of the accident,

211
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:59,090
so you should be able to use it
as evidence.

212
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:02,230
But Dad, did you suspect
Chae Hwa Young too?

213
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,990
How did you think to record it?

214
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:07,630
My phone was set to auto-record calls.

215
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:11,970
I trusted Chae Hwa Young completely,
like a total fool.

216
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:15,110
So I never even thought...

217
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:17,710
to check it.

218
00:12:18,610 --> 00:12:19,640
Thank you.

219
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:22,350
With this crucial evidence,

220
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:26,350
I will make sure Chae Hwa Young
is brought to justice.

221
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:29,220
Actually, your mother...

222
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:34,130
sent me the recording
from Seo Rin's surgery.

223
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:38,330
After hearing those horrible sounds,
my blood ran cold.

224
00:12:38,930 --> 00:12:42,670
I realized I've lived my life all wrong.
I've been so wrong about people.

225
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:44,970
I regretted it all.

226
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:57,350
Nam Bong. What are you doing here?

227
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:59,680
I came to give something to Oh Jang Mi.

228
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:02,950
We need to talk.

229
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,690
What is going on?

230
00:13:06,490 --> 00:13:08,860
What did you give to Oh Jang Mi?

231
00:13:09,890 --> 00:13:11,960
Why? Does it hit a nerve?

232
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:15,670
Nam Bong, don't be so angry.

233
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:19,440
You were the one who started the fight
with me that day.

234
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:23,870
Couples fight and make up.
That's how love deepens.

235
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:26,440
Don't be so upset.

236
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:30,050
You've been gaslighting me
with these tactics,

237
00:13:30,410 --> 00:13:31,650
but not anymore.

238
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:33,250
The rose-colored glasses are off,

239
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:36,320
and I see you for who you really are.

240
00:13:36,690 --> 00:13:37,760
What did you say?

241
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:39,020
Just stop.

242
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,990
You should at least get on your knees
and beg for forgiveness now...

243
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:44,030
for what you did
to Oh Jang Mi and her family.

244
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,760
That's if you're human at all.

245
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:48,400
Are you crazy?

246
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:51,470
Unbelievable...

247
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:54,340
- How dare you raise your hand to me?
- Kang Nam Bong!

248
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:56,340
What did I do wrong to have to beg?

249
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:59,380
What did you hear from that little brat,
Oh Jang Mi?

250
00:13:59,710 --> 00:14:01,710
She got to you, didn't she?

251
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,150
What did she say to convince you?

252
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:05,420
What could she have said
to make you tell me to apologize?

253
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,890
Chae Hwa Young, just stop it already.

254
00:14:08,350 --> 00:14:10,990
I should have known what kind
of person you were from the start.

255
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:14,730
I was such an idiot,
and I deeply regret it.

256
00:14:14,930 --> 00:14:17,060
- I regret it so, so much.
- Shut up!

257
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:18,430
No matter what anyone said,

258
00:14:18,430 --> 00:14:22,930
I thought you were a goddess,
always shining in my heart.

259
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:25,540
All this time, I turned a deaf ear
and a blind eye,

260
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:28,470
and I was a complete fool
for trusting you so blindly.

261
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,670
I feel like bashing my head
against a wall.

262
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:32,010
What did I do?

263
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:34,750
Is this pathetic display
what you call love?

264
00:14:35,310 --> 00:14:37,150
Whether I murder someone or commit fraud,

265
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:39,780
or if the sky falls
and the earth crumbles,

266
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:41,750
you're supposed
to be on my side and support me.

267
00:14:41,990 --> 00:14:43,290
That's what real love is.

268
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:46,660
Isn't it?
That's what real love is, isn't it?

269
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:50,630
As if stealing someone else's newborn baby
wasn't enough,

270
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:53,730
you raised her for over 30 years
only to kill her?

271
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:57,370
You're a piece of trash,
incapable of love or motherly affection.

272
00:14:57,640 --> 00:15:01,540
You're a murderer who'll kill anyone
if they get in your way.

273
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:04,070
Is that your idea of love?

274
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:06,480
If that's the case,
then from the very beginning,

275
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:09,650
I never loved that murderous devil.

276
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:10,810
Never!

277
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:14,390
Hey, Kang Nam Bong!

278
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:16,850
You think you're so great?

279
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:19,190
I regret meeting you too.

280
00:15:19,190 --> 00:15:21,290
You think you're the only one
who regrets it? So do I!

281
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:27,670
Are you going to report this?

282
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:32,370
This person was completely drunk,
just lying in the middle of the road.

283
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:35,140
He seems to be alive,
so I need to call an ambulance now.

284
00:15:35,370 --> 00:15:36,410
An ambulance?

285
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:39,340
But what if he's already dead?

286
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:42,810
What if the police ask you
what you were doing there?

287
00:15:42,950 --> 00:15:43,980
I promise...

288
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:47,220
I'll make sure
you're not implicated in this.

289
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:50,350
Chae Hwa Young orchestrated
the whole thing.

290
00:15:50,650 --> 00:15:53,560
How could she gaslight him
so calmly in that situation?

291
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:56,290
Chae Hwa Young
must have been hiding nearby,

292
00:15:56,290 --> 00:15:58,060
watching the whole thing unfold.

293
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:01,330
She must've panicked when Professor Kang
tried to call the police,

294
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:02,470
so she called him.

295
00:16:02,530 --> 00:16:06,170
Maybe that's why she kept her hooks
in Professor Kang.

296
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:09,040
She was afraid he would tell the truth.

297
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:10,870
If we take the date this was recorded...

298
00:16:11,610 --> 00:16:13,980
and compare it to the cell tower data
from the scene of the accident,

299
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:16,050
Chae Hwa Young's fake alibi
will be shattered.

300
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:18,850
Still, it took a lot of courage
for Professor Kang to do this.

301
00:16:19,650 --> 00:16:20,880
If this file gets out,

302
00:16:21,290 --> 00:16:24,760
he won't be able to escape
legal consequences either.

303
00:16:24,990 --> 00:16:28,090
But it's unfair to Baek Ho's father.

304
00:16:28,990 --> 00:16:30,530
He wasn't speeding,

305
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:33,060
and my dad was lying
on a dark country road.

306
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:35,070
He saw him too late to avoid the accident.

307
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,040
That's right.

308
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,440
Plus, he didn't run away.

309
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:42,140
He called an ambulance, tried to help,
and even turned himself in.

310
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:43,670
So...

311
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:46,110
doesn't that basically make him innocent?

312
00:16:46,380 --> 00:16:50,150
Legally, covering up
someone else's criminal case...

313
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:53,220
by lying to investigators
and confusing the case...

314
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:54,750
is a serious felony.

315
00:16:55,090 --> 00:16:56,450
Depending on the circumstances,

316
00:16:56,450 --> 00:16:58,760
a charge of Obstruction of Official Duties
can be added.

317
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:03,560
He could even face prison time
as an accomplice.

318
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:07,630
Professor Kang knew he could go to jail.

319
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,770
But for Baek Ho and us,

320
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:12,900
he decided to let everything go
and turn himself in.

321
00:17:16,510 --> 00:17:20,080
Mom, are we going to live here now?
Is this our house?

322
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,810
It's not our house.

323
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:23,410
That's not true, Bo Ra.

324
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:26,050
If it's Grandma's house,
it's your house too.

325
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:28,690
We're all going to live here together.

326
00:17:28,890 --> 00:17:30,350
This is so exciting.

327
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:32,120
This house is really nice, Mom.

328
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:33,920
It's amazing, isn't it?

329
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:37,830
There are only a few days left.

330
00:17:38,630 --> 00:17:40,400
It'll all be over on the day
of the founding anniversary event.

331
00:17:41,170 --> 00:17:43,600
As soon as we confirm the deposit
at the banquet hall,

332
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:44,700
we'll get out of there.

333
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,100
We'll go abroad,

334
00:17:46,540 --> 00:17:49,440
- and live in style.
- Timing will be everything.

335
00:17:50,370 --> 00:17:52,340
Once we confirm the money
has been deposited,

336
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:54,810
it'll be a race against the clock
with the IRS.

337
00:17:54,910 --> 00:17:57,610
Right. We have to leave as soon as
the money is deposited.

338
00:17:57,980 --> 00:18:00,580
Then you can check it on your app
at the banquet hall, ma'am.

339
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:03,220
We'll have to drive to get to the airport.

340
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:06,260
If we take my car,
they'll know where we're going right away.

341
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:07,990
I'll have a rental car ready.

342
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:09,960
Okay, Jun Ho. Thank you.

343
00:18:10,990 --> 00:18:12,600
Oh Jang Mi and Kang Baek Ho...

344
00:18:12,930 --> 00:18:15,970
will never think that
we're about to skip town.

345
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,270
- Right?
- Jun Ho.

346
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:22,970
Finally, the three of us can be
a proper family and live well together.

347
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:25,410
You can do whatever you want there,
Jun Ho.

348
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,080
Your mom and I will support you.

349
00:18:30,610 --> 00:18:32,680
That's enough.
It's too early to talk about that.

350
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:34,920
When Oh Jang Mi and the rest...

351
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:37,750
find out Dream is just an empty shell,

352
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:39,220
they're going to be furious.

353
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:43,090
I'm glad I managed to grab this bag...

354
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:46,700
before Chae Hwa Young got kicked out,

355
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:47,900
- Mom.
- What?

356
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,670
What's going to happen to us now?

357
00:18:50,130 --> 00:18:52,970
Oh Jang Mi's family has just moved in
and made themselves at home.

358
00:18:53,140 --> 00:18:56,310
- Does that mean we have to leave or what?
- Leave? We're not going anywhere.

359
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:58,580
We're absolutely not leaving.

360
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:02,610
I'm the Chairman's wife.
So what does that mean?

361
00:19:02,610 --> 00:19:05,580
I'm Jung Suk Hee's stepmother
and Oh Jang Mi's grandmother.

362
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:08,090
If they tell us to leave
when we are this close,

363
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:09,820
they'll be asking for trouble.

364
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:13,790
Keep standing your ground, okay?
I'm counting on you, Mom.

365
00:19:13,890 --> 00:19:15,030
Darn it.

366
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:20,060
You helped cause the Chairman to collapse.
How am I supposed to stand my ground?

367
00:19:20,130 --> 00:19:23,770
And you said
Jang Mi knows about it, right?

368
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:26,040
That's not certain yet.

369
00:19:26,300 --> 00:19:27,970
What am I going to do?

370
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:32,610
- Oh, you've really done it now.
- That hurts!

371
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:43,050
Have all the guests arrived
at the banquet hall?

372
00:19:43,050 --> 00:19:44,890
Yes, they're all waiting.

373
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:47,620
- What about Chairman Martin?
- He's on his way with his wife.

374
00:19:48,330 --> 00:19:49,430
That's ridiculous.

375
00:19:49,790 --> 00:19:51,860
Does he plan on celebrating
his wedding anniversary with his wife...

376
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:53,960
at the company's founding
anniversary event?

377
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:58,040
Still, he seems pretty excited
to be the new owner of Dream.

378
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:01,040
I couldn't care less.

379
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,610
We sold everything we could, right?

380
00:20:08,410 --> 00:20:11,210
Yes. Down to the very last penny,

381
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:13,820
I sold all of your assets
and my own real estate,

382
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,420
and filled up that bag.

383
00:20:15,490 --> 00:20:17,220
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

384
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:20,120
Right. As soon as we get the money
from Martin,

385
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:22,560
we grab this bag and leave immediately.

386
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,630
Hwa Young.

387
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:26,630
Are you okay?

388
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,830
- With what?
- You've had to let go of your dream...

389
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:34,640
- of owning Dream.
- No. I did own Dream.

390
00:20:35,210 --> 00:20:37,240
I'm just leaving the empty shell behind.

391
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,580
The real prize is going into my pocket.

392
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:41,580
I would never give...

393
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:43,680
Oh Jang Mi and Jung Suk Hee Dream,

394
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:45,150
which I poured my blood, sweat,
and tears into.

395
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:49,950
Right. Oh Jang Mi and Jung Suk Hee,
who were always threatening me...

396
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:52,020
to make me pay for my sins,

397
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,990
I'm going to make this
the best day of their lives.

398
00:20:55,730 --> 00:20:58,630
We'll let them party all they want
with the empty shell of Dream,

399
00:20:59,260 --> 00:21:00,800
and we'll make a grand exit.

400
00:21:02,730 --> 00:21:04,740
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

401
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:10,440
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

402
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:32,100
(Dream Hotel 31St Founding Anniversary)

403
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:38,170
(Dream Hotel Casino And Duty-Free Shop
Contract Finalized)

404
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:50,050
To our respected Dream Hotel family,

405
00:21:50,810 --> 00:21:52,580
and to our distinguished guests.

406
00:21:53,650 --> 00:21:56,390
As we celebrate the founding anniversary
of our Dream Hotel,

407
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:59,020
I thank you for taking the time
from your busy schedules to join us...

408
00:21:59,290 --> 00:22:01,090
and share in our celebration.

409
00:22:01,730 --> 00:22:05,600
Recently, our Dream Hotel
has faced an unexpected crisis,

410
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:08,730
and I know many of you
were very concerned.

411
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:12,240
However, with every crisis
comes an opportunity...

412
00:22:17,570 --> 00:22:19,710
After working day and night tirelessly,

413
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:22,780
I finally found a partner who recognized
the value of our Dream.

414
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:25,980
He is a world-renowned,
high-net-worth investor.

415
00:22:26,580 --> 00:22:29,620
As of today, with its global casino
and duty-free shop,

416
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:33,920
Dream will be reborn as a top landmark
that will capture the world's attention.

417
00:22:43,770 --> 00:22:45,600
Hong Ju, I need to use the restroom.

418
00:22:46,340 --> 00:22:47,570
Hurry back.

419
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,670
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

420
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:52,510
And at the heart of this
miraculous comeback...

421
00:22:52,780 --> 00:22:55,080
is a savior who had faith
in our Dream Hotel during the crisis...

422
00:22:55,350 --> 00:22:59,280
and invested in us without hesitation.

423
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,820
He's the chairman
of a world-renowned corporation.

424
00:23:02,150 --> 00:23:06,220
Please welcome Chairman Martin Jang
and his elegant wife.

425
00:23:06,690 --> 00:23:09,160
Please give them a warm round of applause.

426
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:23,210
Everyone, Chairman Martin Jang...

427
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:27,880
What?

428
00:23:28,450 --> 00:23:31,380
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

429
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,750
That's Martin Jang?

430
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:42,090
Dong Seok?

431
00:23:42,930 --> 00:23:47,100
No, this can't be.
But I was told Ma Dong Seok was dead.

432
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:49,630
Then does that mean he's not dead?

433
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,840
Is Martin Jang really Ma Dong Seok?

434
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:12,490
What is going on?

435
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:17,660
Is that really Ma Dong Seok?
How can Ma Dong Seok be Martin Jang?

436
00:24:17,930 --> 00:24:21,100
- I have no idea what's going on either.
- What do you mean you don't know?

437
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:22,530
CEO Chae.

438
00:24:23,930 --> 00:24:25,540
Are you surprised to see me here?

439
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,740
Don't be so surprised.

440
00:24:28,170 --> 00:24:31,410
You met me not long ago when I was Ali.

441
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:34,540
How could you fall for it twice?

442
00:24:35,410 --> 00:24:38,450
- How could you...
- Regardless, a contract is a contract.

443
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,180
I'll send you the kickback you asked for.

444
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,490
Distinguished guests,

445
00:24:45,290 --> 00:24:48,590
the man who will make our Dream Hotel
the best in Asia,

446
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:51,490
Chairman Martin Jang,
will now deliver his remarks.

447
00:25:01,470 --> 00:25:04,510
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

448
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:06,080
Hello, everyone.

449
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,810
I am Martin Jang,
the one who will be in charge of Dream...

450
00:25:09,610 --> 00:25:10,750
from now on.

451
00:25:11,050 --> 00:25:12,120
Ma Dong Seok...

452
00:25:13,050 --> 00:25:15,390
came here knowing we tried to kill him.

453
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,790
We have to get out of here right now.

454
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:21,490
There's a back entrance.

455
00:25:22,130 --> 00:25:23,330
This way. Quickly.

456
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:38,070
Distinguished guests,
please turn your attention...

457
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,180
to CEO Chae Hwa Young,
who's trying to flee.

458
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:41,750
What? She's trying to flee?

459
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:43,810
What are you talking about?

460
00:25:44,150 --> 00:25:46,180
What do you mean, I'm trying to flee?

461
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:48,320
(Confidential Agreement)

462
00:25:48,390 --> 00:25:50,820
CEO Chae made a deal to sell
Dream Hotel's key assets,

463
00:25:50,890 --> 00:25:53,390
the casino and luxury boutiques,
for pennies on the dollar.

464
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:55,930
In return,
she signed a secret contract to pocket...

465
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:57,730
a 300-million-dollar kickback.

466
00:25:57,890 --> 00:26:00,530
This action caused immense damage
to the shareholders...

467
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:03,800
and is a clear-cut case
of breach of fiduciary duty.

468
00:26:04,100 --> 00:26:06,800
What? She tried to take the kickback
for herself?

469
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,840
That's no different
than selling off our company...

470
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:11,980
and leaving us with an empty shell!

471
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:16,210
That's not true.

472
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:20,920
He's an impostor.
A con artist posing as Martin Jang.

473
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:22,950
Everyone, please look at the screen.

474
00:26:24,490 --> 00:26:27,290
How dare you cause a scene, you old man?

475
00:26:27,290 --> 00:26:29,230
You should just quietly leave in peace.

476
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:36,630
Do you think you can get away with this?

477
00:26:37,100 --> 00:26:40,800
Did you forget there is CCTV
all over this house?

478
00:26:41,040 --> 00:26:42,140
CCTV?

479
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,040
Don't you know I control them?

480
00:26:46,010 --> 00:26:48,450
Unfortunately,
they aren't recording right now.

481
00:26:48,450 --> 00:26:49,510
What a shame.

482
00:26:49,980 --> 00:26:53,780
So what is it that you want?

483
00:26:55,020 --> 00:26:56,050
Money?

484
00:26:57,150 --> 00:26:58,150
No.

485
00:26:58,920 --> 00:26:59,960
I want...

486
00:27:00,560 --> 00:27:01,960
your life, Ma Dae Chang.

487
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:05,660
- What?
- Because today is the day you die.

488
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:09,500
- So state your last words.
- What? What did you just say?

489
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:13,670
It's starting to take effect.

490
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:16,640
You took your daily medication today,
didn't you?

491
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:19,680
It's fatal for you.

492
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:22,150
The medicine you've been taking...

493
00:27:22,150 --> 00:27:23,950
is a powerful diuretic...

494
00:27:24,150 --> 00:27:25,750
that looks just like
your blood pressure pills.

495
00:27:26,380 --> 00:27:27,820
The effects have built up,

496
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:31,760
and it's having an explosive reaction
with the medication you took today.

497
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:34,290
No. That footage is fake.

498
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:36,030
It's fabricated to frame me.

499
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:38,030
Why would I harm the Chairman?

500
00:27:38,090 --> 00:27:39,430
Don't be ridiculous.

501
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:42,700
Everyone, don't be fooled.

502
00:27:43,930 --> 00:27:44,970
A kickback?

503
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,870
She was going to take the whole thing?

504
00:27:49,470 --> 00:27:50,610
This is so weird.

505
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:52,840
What's going on?

506
00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:58,680
(Dream Hotel 31st Founding Anniversary)

507
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:03,720
I'm not Ma Seo Rin.

508
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,060
I am her twin sister,

509
00:28:06,860 --> 00:28:08,060
Oh Jang Mi.

510
00:28:46,330 --> 00:28:47,960
(The First Man)

511
00:28:48,130 --> 00:28:49,230
I was wrong.

512
00:28:49,230 --> 00:28:52,700
I said I was wrong.
I was a madman out of my mind.

513
00:28:52,770 --> 00:28:55,670
I'm so sorry.
Please, just forgive me this once.

514
00:28:56,370 --> 00:28:57,770
Mom.

515
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:59,640
The Chairman's awake.

516
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:02,310
What are you packing for?
We need to get out of here now.

517
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:06,580
You're a monster, worse than an animal.

518
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,990
Chae Hwa Young. You're under arrest
for conspiracy to commit murder...

519
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:10,490
and attempted murder.

520
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:14,220
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
